REQUIREMENTS

This utility relies on Apple's packagemaker cmdline utility; packagemaker is part of the Apple Developer tools. Some features require the Radmind tools be installed.

http://developer.apple.com/
http://rsug.itd.umich.edu/software/radmind/

INSTALL/UNINSTALL

A pair of simple scripts to install and uninstall Boilermaker are provided.

1. Open Terminal.app
2. Type: cd <path to Boilermaker download directory>
3. To install, Type: sudo ./install.sh
4. To uninstall, Type: sudo ./uninstall.sh

-- Brian
